Wawasan Media Sosial|https://wawasankehumasan.blogspot.com/2025/10/wawasan-media-sosial.html|Pembahasan seputar media sosial dalam PR.
Strategi Citra Merek|https://wawasankehumasan.blogspot.com/2025/10/strategi-citra-merek.html|Bagaimana PR membangun citra merek positif.
Hubungan Media dan Publik|https://wawasankehumasan.blogspot.com/2025/10/hubungan-media-dan-publik.html|Peran PR dalam menjalin hubungan efektif dengan media.
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0">
<channel>
  <title>Wawasan Kehumasan</title>
  <link>https://wawasankehumasan.blogspot.com</link>
  <description>Update artikel dan wawasan seputar dunia Kehumasan dan Public Relations.</description>
  <lastBuildDate>{{build_date}}</lastBuildDate>
  {{items}}
</channel>
</rss>
from datetime import datetime

def main():
    with open("artikel-pr.txt", "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        lines = [line.strip() for line in f if line.strip()]

    items = ""
    for line in lines:
        try:
            title, link, desc = line.split("|")
            item = f"""
  <item>
    <title>{title.strip()}</title>
    <link>{link.strip()}</link>
    <description>{desc.strip()}</description>
    <pubDate>{datetime.now().strftime('%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S +0700')}</pubDate>
  </item>"""
            items += item
        except ValueError:
            continue

    with open("feed_template.xml", "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        template = f.read()

    output = template.replace("{{items}}", items)
    output = output.replace("{{build_date}}", datetime.now().strftime('%a, %d %b %Y %H:%M:%S +0700'))

    with open("feed.xml", "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        f.write(output)

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
